<p>Swapnil Sinha joined the Imperial Auto board in 2022 and serves on various board committees including the audit committee. Mr Sinha is a Principal at Warburg Pincus and joined the investment firm in 2016. Prior to joining Warburg Pincus, Mr. Sinha worked in the investment banking practice at Barclays in London. Mr. Sinha focuses on investments in the Industrials, TMT and Real Estate sectors. He is currently a Director of Imperial Auto Industries, Good Host Spaces, and R Retail Ventures, and previously served on the boards of Embassy Industrial Parks, and CleanMax Enviro Solutions. Mr. Sinha holds a B.Tech in Mechanical Engineering from Indian Institute of Technology Delhi, and an MBA (with Hons.) from The University of Chicago Booth School of Business.</p>
